{"tid":155009,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本將派國內最大戰艦 於南海巡邏3個月","createTime":"2017-03-13T16:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T00:48:22.000Z","uid":60545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a323945f3088433e98285fda9899e4076c92c594","tid":155009,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:55:08.000Z","msg":"〔編譯周柏憲／綜合報導〕中國聲稱擁有南海絕大部分海域，並在南海增加軍事部署，引發日本以及西方國家關切。美國空、海軍巡弋南海，以確保航行自由權；在日本方面，3名消息人士向《路透》透露，日方計畫派遣國內最大型戰艦至南海，自今年5月開始展開為期3個月的巡航。<br />\n<br />\n消息指出，僅服役2年的日本海上自衛隊的直升機護衛艦「出雲號」（Izumo）將停靠新加坡、印尼、菲律賓、接著去斯里蘭卡，並於7月與美、印的戰艦集結，參與代號「馬拉巴爾」（Malabar）的印度洋海上聯合軍事演習，於8月歸國。<br />\n<br />\n未授權向媒體發言而要求不具名的消息人士也表示，「出雲號」此行目的，除了透過執行長期任務測試「出雲號」的能耐外，也將與美國海軍在南海訓練。<br />\n<br />\n一名日本海上自衛隊的發言人拒絕評論。<br />\n出雲號全長249公尺，體積與日本二戰時期的航母相當，最多可搭載9輛直升機，與美國海軍使用的兩棲突擊艦（amphibious assault carriers）相似，但缺乏兩棲突擊艦供登陸艇駛出的「井圍甲板」（Well deck）。<br />\n<br />\n路透分析，日本近幾年，特別是在日本首相安倍晉三的領導下，不斷挑戰日本戰後「和平憲法」的限制，如「出雲號」被定位為護衛艦，是因為日本憲法禁止收購攻擊性武器；儘管如此，這艘戰艦仍可讓日本在其領土之外展現軍事力量。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2003172\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2003172&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC6S6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=7a1b0d44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2003172&h=d3e653b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2003172</a>"},{"pid":"17fa544d20c4985f4218723cd747e43f47790f9a","tid":155009,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:56:14.000Z","msg":"抵制日本"},{"pid":"6ac42e190d86e37bfe00d5b8368681b6d517e0e2","tid":155009,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:57:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抵制日本</blockquote><br />\n何時抵制香港?"},{"pid":"fd3459ad5d61ba4c12c17ba713c8a5d927640d08","tid":155009,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T17:00:30.000Z","msg":"打鳩我吖， 打鳩我吖， 我成日去南海㗎<br />\n嚟啦打鳩我吖， 啦啦啦啦"},{"pid":"3d7f4be7e6056f9675f3bd00c08bc797eb523938","tid":155009,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T17:19:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5563b26192ad2578867a26fe0429d30b4c009e33","tid":155009,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T18:44:27.000Z","msg":"大日本帝國海軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8172bb2a9e4d4c7acad41d3b1e9696397c460bde","tid":155009,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T18:47:48.000Z","msg":"反完泡又要反日 真忙"},{"pid":"a5c9b9a4485a630ba22cff47a30221428a80b2fd","tid":155009,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:47:32.000Z","msg":"反緊韓又要反日 堅忙"},{"pid":"03e320f685289b21b5abbab025629ae3ae4ddabb","tid":155009,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:48:22.000Z","msg":"大和號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}